A new template was found, where the idea is you need to distribute or create k subarray from an array in such a way
that the difference is minimum. 
Then you need to return the maximum of the values of k distributions which will be the minimum time.


The problems on leetcode of this template.


2305. Fair Distribution of Cookies - https://leetcode.com/problems/fair-distribution-of-cookies/description/
1723. Find Minimum Time to Finish All Jobs - https://leetcode.com/problems/find-minimum-time-to-finish-all-jobs/